{"id":98,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":98,"title":"D&C 94","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 94"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet, at Kirtland, Ohio, August 2, 1833. Hyrum Smith, Reynolds Cahoon, and Jared Carter are appointed as a Church building committee."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.1-9"},"1–9"],", The Lord gives a commandment relative to the erection of a house for the work of the Presidency;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.10-12"},"10–12"],", A printing house is to be built;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.13-17"},"13–17"],", Certain inheritances are assigned."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.1","order":"06.05.094.12083"},["b","1"],"And again, verily I say unto you, my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"friends"],", a commandment I give unto you, that ye shall commence a work of laying out and preparing a beginning and foundation of the city of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"stake"],"of Zion, here in the land of Kirtland, beginning at my house."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.2","order":"06.05.094.12084"},["b","2"],"And behold, it must be done according to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"pattern"],"which I have given unto you."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.3","order":"06.05.094.12085"},["b","3"],"And let the first lot on the south be consecrated unto me for the building of a house for the presidency, for the work of the presidency, in obtaining revelations; and for the work of the ministry of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"presidency"],", in all things pertaining to the church and kingdom."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.4","order":"06.05.094.12086"},["b","4"],"Verily I say unto you, that it shall be built fifty-five by sixty-five feet in the width thereof and in the length thereof, in the inner court."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.5","order":"06.05.094.12087"},["b","5"],"And there shall be a lower court and a higher court, according to the pattern which shall be given unto you hereafter."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.6","order":"06.05.094.12088"},["b","6"],"And it shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"dedicated"],"unto the Lord from the foundation thereof, according to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"order"],"of the priesthood, according to the pattern which shall be given unto you hereafter."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.7","order":"06.05.094.12089"},["b","7"],"And it shall be wholly dedicated unto the Lord for the work of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"presidency"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.8","order":"06.05.094.12090"},["b","8"],"And ye shall not suffer any",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"unclean thing"],"to come in unto it; and my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"glory"],"shall be there, and my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"presence"],"shall be there."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.9","order":"06.05.094.12091"},["b","9"],"But if there shall come into it any",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"unclean thing"],", my glory shall not be there; and my presence shall not come into it."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.10","order":"06.05.094.12092"},["b","10"],"And again, verily I say unto you, the second lot on the south shall be dedicated unto me for the building of a house unto me, for the work of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"printing"],"of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"translation of my scriptures"],", and all things whatsoever I shall command you."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.11","order":"06.05.094.12093"},["b","11"],"And it shall be fifty-five by sixty-five feet in the width thereof and the length thereof, in the inner court; and there shall be a lower and a higher court."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.12","order":"06.05.094.12094"},["b","12"],"And this house shall be wholly dedicated unto the Lord from the foundation thereof, for the work of the printing, in all things whatsoever I shall command you, to be holy, undefiled, according to the pattern in all things as it shall be given unto you."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.13","order":"06.05.094.12095"},["b","13"],"And on the third lot shall my servant Hyrum Smith receive his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"inheritance"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.14","order":"06.05.094.12096"},["b","14"],"And on the first and second lots on the north shall my servants Reynolds Cahoon and Jared Carter receive their inheritances—"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.15","order":"06.05.094.12097"},["b","15"],"That they may do the work which I have appointed unto them, to be a committee to build mine houses, according to the commandment, which I, the Lord God, have given unto you."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.16","order":"06.05.094.12098"},["b","16"],"These two houses are not to be built until I give unto you a commandment concerning them."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.17","order":"06.05.094.12099"},["b","17"],"And now I give unto you no more at this time. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.1a","order":"06.05.094.12100"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.45"},"D&C 93:45"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.1b","order":"06.05.094.12102"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/68.26"},"D&C 68:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/82.13"},"82:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/96.1"},"96:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/104.48"},"104:48"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.59"},"109:59"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.2a","order":"06.05.094.12104"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/8.5"},"Heb. 8:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/52.14"},"D&C 52:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/95.14"},"95:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/97.10"},"97:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/115.14.14-16"},"115:14 (14–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.3a","order":"06.05.094.12106"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.9.8-78"},"D&C 107:9 (8–78)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.6a","order":"06.05.094.12108"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dedication"},"TG Dedication"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sacred"},"Sacred"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.6b","order":"06.05.094.12110"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/6.32"},"1 Chr. 6:32"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.7a","order":"06.05.094.12112"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.9.8-78"},"D&C 107:9 (8–78)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.8a","order":"06.05.094.12114"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.46.46-48"},"Luke 19:46 (46–48)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.20.19-20"},"D&C 109:20 (19–20)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/uncleanness"},"TG Uncleanness"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.8b","order":"06.05.094.12116"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/8.11.10-11"},"1 Kgs. 8:11 (10–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/43.2"},"Ezek. 43:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.25"},"D&C 101:25"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/glory"},"TG Glory"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.8c","order":"06.05.094.12118"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-presence-of"},"TG God, Presence of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.9a","order":"06.05.094.12120"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/15.31"},"Lev. 15:31"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/90.18"},"D&C 90:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/97.15"},"97:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.10a","order":"06.05.094.12122"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/104.58"},"D&C 104:58"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-writing-of"},"TG Scriptures, Writing of"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.10b","order":"06.05.094.12124"},["b","10b"],["span.small","IE"],"the translation of the Bible.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.53"},"D&C 93:53"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.89"},"124:89"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.13a","order":"06.05.094.12126"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/inheritance"},"TG Inheritance"],". See also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/triple-index/inherit"},"“Inherit” in Index"],"."]]}
